name: Corner extends Cublet
description: A Corner is the type of Cublet that has 3 colors and sits on the corners of the cube. There are 8 corners on the cube.

methods.name: Corner()
methods.description: Constructs a Corner given its solved position (x, y, z), and its orientation.

methods.name: twistClockwise()
methods.description: Returns a new Corner representing this Corner twisted clockwise

methods.name: twistCounterClockwise()
methods.description: Returns a new Corner representing this Corner twisted counter-clockwise
